{"tid":1763630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財務緊張？華為不到1年 融資逾35億美元","createTime":"2019-11-30T13:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T14:05:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e17029d0fa23768a05a116c2d8b06b4eba2a00","tid":1763630,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"財務緊張？華為不到1年 融資逾1000億元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2993667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2993667&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=812e0596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2993667&h=17a894b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2993667</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯楊芙宜／台北報導〕彭博新聞報導，知情人士透露，中國華為公司（Huawei）現正在尋求籌集折合約15億美元的離岸貸款，該公司今年7月份才敲定一筆117億港元（約14.9億美元）貸款，不到半年內又第2度尋求融資；彭博彙整數據顯示，華為在不到1年內已貸款融資達35億美元（約1074億台幣）。外界關注華為是否面臨資金缺口的財務緊張。<br />\n<br />\n中國電信設備和智慧手機大廠華為遭到美國制裁，被列入華府出口管制的貿易黑名單，並禁止美國電信商使用聯邦補貼採購其設備，等於遭到美國「禁售和禁買」的雙重制裁。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士表示，華為再次尋求15億美元貸款，正就這筆貸款安排與國際國內銀行展開洽談，由華為投資控股出具將同意盡力協助的告慰函（letter of comfort）；華為籌得的資金將主要用於營運資金和一般企業用途。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">華為對外稱「不缺錢」，近1年來卻頻頻在中國及海外貸款融資。華為7月向5家中資銀行貸款融資117億港元，是華為在貸款市場上的第一筆無國際銀行插手的離岸融資；更早在2018年12月還曾簽署了一筆140億元人民幣（約616億台幣）的在岸貸款。<br />\n<br />\n此外，今年10月，華為還首次境內發行債券。上海清算所數據顯示，華為債券發行總額30億人民幣，殖利率3.48%。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"674d7e84a256e95278e7510043c9e2cb17514c05","tid":1763630,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"老共支持點會缺錢<br />\n印都印到俾佢啦⋯⋯"},{"pid":"885016df23b385b3915c9ca4aa19cbc1193623b6","tid":1763630,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"674d7e84a256e95278e7510043c9e2cb17514c05","tid":1763630,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"老共支持點會缺錢<br />\n印都印到俾佢啦⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"或者反轉諗，佢地攞錢俾支那"},{"pid":"3e24bd923daee64aefdb3a780c01b6e3650ca0a2","tid":1763630,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885016df23b385b3915c9ca4aa19cbc1193623b6","tid":1763630,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"674d7e84a256e95278e7510043c9e2cb17514c05","tid":1763630,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"老共支持點會缺錢<br />\n印都印到俾佢啦⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"或者反轉諗，佢地攞錢俾支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"要外滙 呢排支為算係支國海外最成功brand啦"},{"pid":"3eed76fa6e46663efc6f6f1deeeec6339797b0b7","tid":1763630,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"華為停左幾個月賣唔到機<br />\n唔死已經奇蹟<br />\n<br />\ngoogle 整佢應該好傷"},{"pid":"36bb7f158dbabb37ca8a9b1514cf630b6b08258b","tid":1763630,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"相比從來都唔洗借錢的蘋果，高下立見！"},{"pid":"3218dca691be064f14152f27c8d9238a5c3d81e7","tid":1763630,"uid":97078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"35億好少姐"},{"pid":"0f5032df31c2bab256222a31c041baa2afae6125","tid":1763630,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"華為要外匯者<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7550c57d5a170f73705f414e5d5aeed2aa4808","tid":1763630,"uid":60200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36bb7f158dbabb37ca8a9b1514cf630b6b08258b","tid":1763630,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"相比從來都唔洗借錢的蘋果，高下立見！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"蘋果有發債的"}]}